originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_brand, 
    p.p_type, 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue
FROM 
    lineitem l
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON l.l_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    r.r_name = 'ASIA'
    AND l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'
    AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1995-02-01'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_brand, p.p_type
ORDER BY 
    revenue DESC

FROM 
    lineitem l
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON l.l_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    r.r_name = 'ASIA'
    AND l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'
    AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1995-02-01'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_brand, p.p_type
ORDER BY 
    revenue DESC

SELECT COALESCE("part"."p_brand", "part"."p_brand") AS "P_BRAND", "part"."p_type" AS "P_TYPE", SUM("t0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t0"."l_discount")) AS "REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "region"
WHERE "r_name" = 'ASIA') AS "t"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "t"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" < DATE '1995-02-01') AS "t0" INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "t0"."l_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "part"."p_brand", "part"."p_type"
